# Implementation Plan — Receipt Language Settings (Hindi / English / Bilingual)

This plan details the implementation of a Receipt Language setting. Users can configure the language for print receipts under **Settings → Store Info**. All customer bills will automatically print using English, Hindi, or Bilingual labels depending on this store setting.

## User Review Required

> [!NOTE]
> - **Product Names**: As specified, product names (e.g., *"Aashirvaad Shudh Chakki Atta 5kg"*) will remain in English. Only the receipt labels, headers, and brand name will translate.
> - **Bilingual Mode Layout**: In bilingual mode, labels will render in the format `Hindi / English` (e.g., `बिल नं. / Bill No:`).

